---
import Container from '@components/container.astro'
import PageTitle from '@components/page-title.astro'
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <Container>
    <PageTitle>
      <Fragment slot="title">Privacy Policy</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">What this site collects, and what it does not.</Fragment>
    </PageTitle>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-10 mx-auto max-w-full mt-12 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        Information You Choose to Send
      </h2>
      <p>
        This site does not have accounts, comments, payments, or a newsletter
        signup. If you use the contact form or send email, you choose to share
        your name, email address, message, and any context you include.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">How Contact Messages Are Used</h2>
      <p>
        Contact messages are used to read and reply to the conversation you
        started. The form is submitted through Web3Forms, a third-party form
        service, so form submissions are also handled by that provider.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
        Analytics
      </h2>
      <p>
        This site uses Umami analytics to understand basic site usage. The goal
        is aggregate signal, not individual tracking. Do not put sensitive
        information into URLs or contact-form messages unless it is necessary
        for the conversation.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        I do not sell, rent, or lease personal information. Information may be
        processed by service providers that make the site work, including
        hosting, analytics, and the contact form provider.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Retention and Control</h2>
      <p>
        I keep contact messages only as long as they are useful for the
        conversation or related records. If you want a message deleted, email me
        and I will handle the request directly.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Changes</h2>
      <p>
        I may update this page when the site changes. Material changes should
        describe the actual behavior of the site rather than relying on generic
        privacy-policy language.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Contact Information</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
        at
        <span>
          <Icon class="inline-flex" name="uil:envelope" />
          <a
            class="font-medium
            text-gray-600
            dark:text-gray-400
            hover:text-blue-500
            dark:hover:text-orange-500
            underline"
            href="mailto:jeremy.c.london@gmail.com"
            >jeremy.c.london@gmail.com
          </a>
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
